              .st-panel__content
                p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
                p Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate.            
          .st-panel
            .st-panel__cont
              .st-panel__header(data-tool="collapse")
                .fluid-cols
                  .expand-col.text-ellipsis
                    span.st-panel__title
                      span Input Bar
                  .min-col
                    .st-panel__form
                      .st-inputbar
                        .st-inputbar-input.hidden-xs
                          input#persons-table-search.form-control.input-sm(type="text", placeholder="Search", style="width: 200px")
                        .st-inputbar-btn
                          .btn-group
                            a.btn.btn-success.btn-sm(href='#') Create
                            button.btn.btn-success.btn-sm.dropdown-toggle(type='button', data-toggle="dropdown", data-container="body")
                              i.caret
                            ul.dropdown-menu.dropdown-menu-right
                              li
                                a(href="#") Delete
                              li
                                a(href="#") Activate
                              li
                                a(href="#") Disable
              .st-panel__content
                .table-responsive.table-responsive-bordered
                  table#persons-table.table.table-bordered.table-hover.table-filled.table-select.table-headless(style="margin-bottom: 0;")
                    thead
                      tr
                        th.content-width #
                        th First Name
                        th Last Name
                        th Status
                    tbody
                      tr
                        td.content-width
                          .checkbox.condensed
                            input#p1(type="checkbox")
                            label(for="p1")
                        td Mark
                        td Otto
                        td.content-width
                          span.label.label-default Active
                      tr
                        td.content-width
                          .checkbox.condensed
                            input#p2(type="checkbox")
                            label(for="p2")
                        td Jacob
                        td Thornton
                        td.content-width
                          span.label.label-default Active
                      tr
                        td.content-width
                          .checkbox.condensed
                            input#p3(type="checkbox")
                            label(for="p3")
                        td Larry
                        td the Bird
                        td.content-width
                          span.label.label-default Disabled
              .st-panel__footer
                .fluid-cols
                  .expand-col.text-ellipsis
                    span#persons-table-info
                  .min-col
                    .st-panel__tools
                      .st-panel-tool(data-tool="resize")
                        i.fa.fa-window-maximize
                      a.st-panel-tool(data-tool="source")
                        i.fa.fa-code
          .st-panel
            .st-panel__cont
              .st-panel__header
                .fluid-cols
                  .expand-col.text-ellipsis
                    span.st-panel__title
                      span Pagination
                  .min-col
                    .st-panel__form
                      ul.pagination.pagination-xs
                        li
                          a(href="#")
                            span &laquo;
                        li
                          a(href="#") 1
                        li
                          a(href="#") 2
                        li
                          a(href="#") 3
                        li
                          a(href="#") 4
                        li
                          a(href="#") 5
                        li
                          a(href="#")
                            span &raquo;
              .st-panel__content
                p Panels could contain various types of elements in their heads. For example, <code>inputs</code>, <code>buttons</code>, <code>labels</code>, <code>pagination</code>. Anything you can fit in 30px height.
          .st-panel
            .st-panel__cont
              .st-panel__content
                p When all you need is just to place some content in the box.
                .st-source.st-source--copy
                  .st-source__copy.st-clip(data-clipboard-target="#box-code") Copy
                  pre
                    code.html#box-code
                      :code
                        <div class="st-panel">
                          <div class="st-panel__cont">
                            <div class="st-panel__content">
                              ..Content..
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
